        In today's landscape, cyber threats are growing at an exponential rate. From ransomware attacks targeting critical infrastructure to state-sponsored espionage, organisations depend on skilled analysts to stay one step ahead. As Malaysia advances its national cybersecurity framework and industries like banking, healthcare, and aviation undergo rapid digital transformation, the demand for qualified cybersecurity professionals has never been higher.
        <br/><br/>
        This role is deeply relevant to my academic background at UniSZA — covering network security, forensics, and penetration testing — giving me a strong foundation to enter this career path with confidence.
      </p>
